<descript>
<abstract>
South Africa Miscellaneous Linear Structures, 2014 is a line theme representing miscellaneous of structures in South Africa.  Atrributes include the feature type (aerial cable way, bridge, conveyor belt, dam wall, pier, power line multiple, power line single, slipway, tunnel, tunnel entrance). The source material is a 1:50,000 topographical map series. The original shapefile was originally created in tiles and were merged together by Columbia Libraries, the original map sheet for each feature is included in the attribute table.
 </abstract>
</descript>
